Package au.edu.anu.omhtk.environment

package au.edu.anu.omhtk.environment
Defines the execution environment of an application. These classes were initially designed for the deployment of big applications on a possibly heterogeneous set of various targets, i.e. computers, clusters, grids. However, the development has stopped when we disovered OpenMole and we never wrote the expected RemoteEnvironment class.
Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 18 mai 2021
